Package ccre.cluck

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CluckChannelListener
    A listener for data sent over a Cluck channel.
    CluckSubscriptionListener
    A listener for which channels on a CluckNode have explicit subscriptions.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CluckEncoder
    A CluckEncoder provides a number of methods for publishing and subscribing to various dynamic objects, such as channels, events, loggers, and holders.
    CluckEncoder.AvailableListener
    An AvailableListener is notified whenever a new object is provided on the network that it did not previously know about.
    CluckGlobals
    A class containing static fields for various Cluck objects.
    CluckNetworkedClient
    A single endpoint of a Cluck connection.
    CluckNetworkedServer
    The server for Cluck, allows clients to connect to it and transfer data.
    CluckNode
    A message router for Cluck.
    StandaloneCluckServer
    A simple standalone cluck server for testing.
